mute: osascript -e 'set volume output muted not (output muted of (get volume settings))'
spotlight-search: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to key code 49 using command down '
close-application-: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to key code 13 using command down'
up: osascript -e 'set volume output volume (output volume of (get volume settings) + 10) --100%'
down: osascript -e 'set volume output volume (output volume of (get volume settings) - 10) --100%'
vscode: osascript -e 'tell application "Visual Studio Code" to activate'
